<p>Since the establishment of the Yamaha Music Foundation in 1966, Yamaha’s world-famous music education system has produced over 5,000,000 graduates in over 40 countries.

<p>And right here in Australia we offer our unique and exciting education system in over 25 schools across the country. Since its inception in Australia 35 years ago, 50,000 Australian children have already developed a life-long love of music through their attendance at a Yamaha Music Education Centre.

