<ul>
	<li>Proven curriculum and teaching method developed not only by musicians but also by world experts in child psychology and early childhood development.</li>
	<li>40 years experience with over 5 million graduates worldwide</li>
	<li>Established in over 40 countries across the globe</li>
	<li>Exciting performance opportunities for students – both in Australia and overseas</li>
	<li>Dedicated teachers who are carefully selected, meticulously trained and receive continuous on-going support from experts in Australia and from around the world</li>
